  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"16ea8b34136bc096fc656acbcf9dd5c3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">记录一些我个人比较看重并且有希望解决的问题，如果您发现这些问题有进展，麻烦提醒我一下。</span></p><p id=\"u7b1ca7cd\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ued168f8e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">PS：仅记录。</span></p><h1 id=\"aTz3P\"><span class=\"ne-text\">思源笔记：略</span></h1><h1 id=\"hKh8e\"><span class=\"ne-text\">logseq：略</span></h1><h1 id=\"b1e219e45f7b65c2d8c4a3b7edfd146a\"><span class=\"ne-text\">VNoteX：引入 SQLite 和 ID</span></h1><h1 id=\"bd2a1c9f66ac8f4fc3bcb8df42a3bea7\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Notion：解决 page 转换为 block 导致链接失效</span></h1><p id=\"aead6c9ace6b906e7fc1d22aa212f5e3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">有希望解决，但是得等很久。在双链功能完善之前，notion 估计根本意识不到这个问题。</span></p><h1 id=\"7397e7b1a786c0b499f634bc62d785eb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">OneNote：2025 年结束之后微软是否继续提供支持</span></h1><h1 id=\"VvqsG\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">思源笔记：容器块聚焦</span></h1><p id=\"u60f27e27\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">已实现。</span></p><h1 id=\"98e25245919704ed385498ad2ab509e3\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">logseq：自定义日记格式</span></h1><p id=\"569d3e806bf02a47ed95162e742439c5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">已解决，可在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">logseq.edn</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\"> 中自定义，也可以直接在设置菜单里定义了。</span></p><h1 id=\"208766d17af0a48a06332ca0f721f4d2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">思源笔记：反向链接取消树状层级</span></h1><p id=\"5562e0dc88494014d8d7be7aa342d291\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">去游说了一下，现已修正。</span></p><h1 id=\"521b0a9f5119283c9e04dc98e6126455\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">logseq：使用本地文件夹 粘贴图片时不再上传图床</span></h1><p id=\"7eb7cf083c045c89f60d84e8533cfec0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">本地文件夹是解决了，但是用 GitHub 仓库时图片还是会上传到 logseq 的图床。</span></p><h1 id=\"496518a42af350ceee61dfbef0690a0e\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">思源笔记：文档与正文之间互相转化，同时保持 id 不变</span></h1><p id=\"4bfb8bda3601f52fbda6bb14bbfc1fc8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">v0.53 发布此功能。</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #CF1322\">牛逼</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">。</span></p><h1 id=\"8d00c31a3a6f2961f8776987c6376a76\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">Obsidian：突出显示指向空内容的链接</span></h1><p id=\"78489793988f851009be329a37a40e60\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">0.9.4 之后已解决，仅在预览模式下有效，网状图谱里也会区别显示。</span></p><h1 id=\"B0q2g\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">org-sanpo：等待可用的版本</span></h1><p id=\"u0ea53f03\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #8C8C8C\">直接用 org-roam v2</span></p><p id=\"80742a87f5f8a15d01607d93ab9f26e8\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></div>",
